---
title: Veggie Stuffed Peppers (v) with Caprese Salad
description: Lizzie’s Italian-inspired stuffed peppers make a filling vegetarian meal and are perfect for those lazy nights in at home. Packed with fresh flavours, topped with cheese and baked until golden and bubbling, they’re as easy to eat as they are to make! Served alongside a classic Caprese salad, this deliciously simple dish is a guaranteed dinner winner the whole family will love
